                    <span>If you are an executive don't fail to read this. Kaplan and Norton's Balanced Scorecard approach has had a tremendous impact on thinking in the executive suite. Buy and read a copy today. I have bought copies for all of my clients.<p>Michael Beitler<br>Author of "Strategic Organizational Change"</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Overblown and impractical</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>2</span>
